# Per-session prompt logs (UserPromptSubmit hook) are gitignored raw — they
# churn every prompt and would nag the stop hook each turn.  Committed only
# after the `prompt-log` cleanup, via `git add -f`.  INDEX.md stays tracked.
prompt-log/*.md
!prompt-log/INDEX.md
